  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to own the world's best laundry store? Transform a small laundry shop into a laundry empire!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the following features in Laundry Store Simulator: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/66d4db01232ed1e0885aaf53ed9eb998.avif?t=1773839525\" width=600 height=89 /></span>Build a small laundry store into a thriving business empire! Upgrade your equipment, design and expand your store, hire staff, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/ef953b48268f06c8467c4b47a0c1cf8c.poster.avif?t=1773839525\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/ef953b48268f06c8467c4b47a0c1cf8c.webm?t=1773839525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/ef953b48268f06c8467c4b47a0c1cf8c.mp4?t=1773839525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/b2cc5ffe361ff570d74453c6c02d112a.avif?t=1773839525\" width=600 height=89 /></span>Upgrade your equipment to provide exceptional cleaning services! Invest in high-quality washing machines, dryers, ironing equipment, and even automated washing machines!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/284829a4413dc13002762ce305c93cf0.poster.avif?t=1773839525\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/284829a4413dc13002762ce305c93cf0.webm?t=1773839525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/284829a4413dc13002762ce305c93cf0.mp4?t=1773839525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/7dca6a108f4175afa1f93452cc6d45a7.avif?t=1773839525\" width=600 height=89 /></span>Create a stylish and inviting space to attract customers! Provide comfortable seating, warm decorations, and more funsies to welcome your customers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/4be0a6e0333ce34bafc6bb29b8d5f857.poster.avif?t=1773839525\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/4be0a6e0333ce34bafc6bb29b8d5f857.webm?t=1773839525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/4be0a6e0333ce34bafc6bb29b8d5f857.mp4?t=1773839525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/e93d2fdc769d6f07a2fb870f73fdde78.avif?t=1773839525\" width=600 height=89 /></span>Grow your laundry business by unlocking new areas and features, offering complimentary services to attract more customers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/ed2bf3314e85f35a5f74e5715ef07c3f.poster.avif?t=1773839525\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/ed2bf3314e85f35a5f74e5715ef07c3f.webm?t=1773839525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/ed2bf3314e85f35a5f74e5715ef07c3f.mp4?t=1773839525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/e0b8e3e8c97e7398ace596001b87a56f.avif?t=1773839525\" width=600 height=89 /></span>Build a dedicated team to manage your laundry store efficiently! Hire qualified and experienced staff laundry attendants, such as, washers, dryers, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/9dadc12254071798c0b7773d5f32dbf4.poster.avif?t=1773839525\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/9dadc12254071798c0b7773d5f32dbf4.webm?t=1773839525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/9dadc12254071798c0b7773d5f32dbf4.mp4?t=1773839525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/3bb8610d6482e1524b5bd43a260ee00d.avif?t=1773839525\" width=600 height=89 /></span>Boost your profits by selling cleaning supplies and becoming a one-stop shop for laundry needs! Offer a variety of cleaning products, including detergents, fabric softeners, stain removers, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/dec238a72832e3a145251a3d777cab23.poster.avif?t=1773839525\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/dec238a72832e3a145251a3d777cab23.webm?t=1773839525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/dec238a72832e3a145251a3d777cab23.mp4?t=1773839525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/4a64bc8e90db4871a62d2104533f1255.avif?t=1773839525\" width=600 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your creativity by designing custom shirts for unique customers! Draw anything, print it, and watch them proudly wear your creations in style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/d4b0deafe366f4535b4dc8037bc7531e.poster.avif?t=1773839525\" width=640 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/d4b0deafe366f4535b4dc8037bc7531e.webm?t=1773839525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/d4b0deafe366f4535b4dc8037bc7531e.mp4?t=1773839525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
